vely.\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"summary_text\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"**Identifying potential issues**\\\\n\\\\nI'm noticing some potential compile issues related to the `default @DiscriminatorMapping`. It seems to be missing parens in the source, which might be an annotation type issue. There’s also a concern regarding the `Content` field having `@Target({ ElementType.FIELD })` but being used nested. Then, `ExternalDocumentation` targets FIELD but appears as default in Operation, which feels a bit strange. However, I see no problem with the required title and version for `@Info`.\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"summary_text\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"**Checking code imports**\\\\n\\\\nI'm thinking that there might be some old packages in the user-code-filter, but I notice there are no test imports mentioned. It seems like the final mention hasn’t run. I should probably check for any differences in the code by looking at `git diff`. This will help me ensure everything is up to date and running smoothly!\\\"}]}\"}, {\"type\": \"toolCall\", \"id\": \"call_HmUZWdjbxu6sw7hWD2hwaTjv|fc_0e4fa27c970806100169f87c8543a481a2a3d34d92691443ba\", \"name\": \"bash\", \"arguments\": {\"command\": \"git diff -- tests/src/io.swagger/swagger-annotations/2.0.0-rc0/src/test/java/io_swagger/swagger_annotations/Swagger_annotationsTest.java | sed -n '1,220p'\", \"timeout\": 60}}], \"api\": \"openai-responses\", \"provider\": \"OCA\", \"model\": \"gpt-5.5\", \"usage\": {\"input\": 387, \"output\": 1136, \"cacheRead\": 57856, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"totalTokens\": 59379, \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"total\": 0}}, \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\", \"timestamp\": 1777892461995, \"responseId\": \"resp_0e4fa27c970806100169f87c6e962481a29ee90290ae007611\"}, \"toolResults\": [{\"role\": \"toolResult\", \"toolCallId\": \"call_HmUZWdjbxu6sw7hWD2hwaTjv|fc_0e4fa27c970806100169f87c8543a481a2a3d34d92691443ba\", \"toolName\": \"bash\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"d